rxin [at] cs.berkeley.edu
vim settings

To use, copy .gvimrc and .vim to ~/ and place the rest of the times in ~/.vim.

Plugins used:

- scala 2.8 plugin (from official scala repo)

- git-vim by motemen
  http://github.com/motemen/git-vim

- gitdiff.vim
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1846

- NERD tree
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1658

- FuzzyFinder
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1984

- L9
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3252

- snipMate
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2540

- scala-vim-snippets by tommoris
  http://github.com/tommorris/scala-vim-snippets

- SuperTab continued.
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=1643

- taglist with hack from stackoverflow
  http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=273
  http://stackoverflow.com/questions/3019691/has-anyone-got-the-vim-taglist-plugin-working-with-scala


